{"tid":1185361,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"市區貴價戶連環蝕讓 尚匯麥花臣匯淪「潛水樓」","createTime":"2019-06-04T08:36:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T04:12:07.000Z","uid":116572,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"dc42ce8fc3572423f39fac387ace5f28b11934de","tid":1185361,"uid":116572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:36:06.000Z","msg":"市區貴價戶樓價長期潛水，導致部份業主心淡決定壯士斷臂，「止血」離場。灣仔尚匯中層B室一房戶以1,050萬元售出，單位實用面積342方呎，呎價30,701元，賣方2011年向恒地(012)以1,007萬元買入，8年升值僅4%，明賺實蝕。另一個市區「潛水樓」旺角麥花臣匯1B座低層H室，實用面積470方呎，一房間隔，業主2015年以884萬元一手買入，剛以880萬元蝕賣，呎價18,723元，買新樓揸四年，連使費竟料蝕46萬元，有樓都未能享受到期間香港樓價升幅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190603/59671475\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190603%2F59671475&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=c6c0ba4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190603%2F59671475&h=2e2bbdda\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190603/59671475</a>"},{"pid":"987cbd88e03ce0d64d0fd163deab76595c3c5e4f","tid":1185361,"uid":226177,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:39:03.000Z","msg":"所以我唔明點解有人會買新樓做投資,俾發展商食你幾年升幅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5db2c3b396684bd7c1f9f94a217be3b1a2246a5","tid":1185361,"uid":52778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:42:15.000Z","msg":"某幾間發展商食哂你幾年升幅"},{"pid":"ee666d43db730bb53a2491a77431c7ec0c5286f4","tid":1185361,"uid":219614,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:50:56.000Z","msg":"你買果陣18000新高<br />\n但你貪9成按全新<br />\n到賣時二手樓6成按，但就要18000起標，緊係難賣"},{"pid":"6ca688b80da6155e4efee8eba4f55c5066547a53","tid":1185361,"uid":165160,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e5db2c3b396684bd7c1f9f94a217be3b1a2246a5","t